column5: Hey there guys I maybe going up to that area for a bit (not that far from home I know) I was wondering if Hand H was still opened for tackle and bait. i'm after a few things and might have a ride there for a day
They are in with their paintball shop, at least they were last time i went. Search H & H paintball
Last time I drove past it appeared to be open. ~2 weeks ago.
They are still open but are located at the original H&H Battery store not at the paintball store. I was in there last week.
there is no tackle left in the paintball place..Try the orignal place, battery- gun shop....
H&H is open, and is located at the original location.  If your looking for something specific i would call first cause i find the shop very hit or miss.
